I can't give you any more than what I can show you here.

1043
00:49:00,040 --> 00:49:05,040
You trusted that we had Merv from the same sort of image.

1044
00:49:05,320 --> 00:49:06,760
I did.

1045
00:49:06,760 --> 00:49:10,400
Which brought you here, so you trusted that much.

1046
00:49:11,320 --> 00:49:13,960
You know Layden Menda, he saved you.

1047
00:49:13,960 --> 00:49:16,040
You did a solid for him.

1048
00:49:16,040 --> 00:49:18,400
He's gonna do what he can to help you now.

1049
00:49:20,120 --> 00:49:21,200
Okay, good.

1050
00:49:21,200 --> 00:49:22,200
Your friends got a problem?

1051
00:49:22,200 --> 00:49:23,480
They look a little antsy.

1052
00:49:24,640 --> 00:49:25,480
Oh, them?

1053
00:49:25,480 --> 00:49:26,320
No, they're cool.

1054
00:49:28,400 --> 00:49:30,720
We're just on kidnap patrol.

1055
00:49:30,720 --> 00:49:32,800
I get kidnapped a lot, you understand.

1056
00:49:32,800 --> 00:49:35,080
I do, I do understand.

1057
00:49:35,080 --> 00:49:39,200
All right, might I have my ball back?

1058
00:49:39,200 --> 00:49:40,600
Oh yeah, for sure.

1059
00:49:40,600 --> 00:49:41,800
Thank you.

1060
00:49:41,800 --> 00:49:43,320
Seen enough?

1061
00:49:43,320 --> 00:49:44,400
Is there more?

1062
00:49:44,400 --> 00:49:46,400
Did you guys give him a fishing boat?

1063
00:49:47,480 --> 00:49:49,200
Why would we give him a fishing boat?

1064
00:49:49,240 --> 00:49:51,560
Well, you know, he was.

1065
00:49:51,560 --> 00:49:52,560
That's not part of the deal.

1066
00:49:52,560 --> 00:49:53,680
I know, I'm just saying.

1067
00:49:53,680 --> 00:49:55,520
He snatches the ball from your hand and says,

1068
00:49:55,520 --> 00:49:58,600
it's been a pleasure doing business with yous.

1069
00:49:58,600 --> 00:49:59,960
Yeah, you too.

1070
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:01,320
Sorry, what's your name, friend?

1071
00:50:01,320 --> 00:50:02,840
Not any of your business.

1072
00:50:02,840 --> 00:50:05,520
Not any of your business, very unique.

1073
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:07,800
He turns and he begins to walk away.

1074
00:50:07,800 --> 00:50:09,960
Safe travels home there, Sullivan Sleight

1075
00:50:09,960 --> 00:50:12,200
and snatch patrol.

1076
00:50:13,560 --> 00:50:14,400
Oh.

1077
00:50:15,360 --> 00:50:18,880
It's a fucking racing name you guys have now.

1078
00:50:18,880 --> 00:50:20,760
Whoa, snatch patrol.

1079
00:50:20,760 --> 00:50:22,160
We gotta head back.

1080
00:50:22,160 --> 00:50:23,880
Head back to High Moon.

1081
00:50:23,880 --> 00:50:24,720
Okay.

1082
00:50:27,200 --> 00:50:30,400
Okay, so that went, I guess, fairly well.

1083
00:50:30,400 --> 00:50:33,400
He showed me a picture, ball, magic ball,

1084
00:50:33,400 --> 00:50:37,160
magic crystal ball that showed me that Merv is safe

1085
00:50:37,160 --> 00:50:38,400
and was let go.

1086
00:50:38,400 --> 00:50:42,400
And I mean, that's cool.

1087
00:50:42,400 --> 00:50:43,320
I'm so glad.

1088
00:50:43,320 --> 00:50:45,400
I really didn't know if we were gonna make it

1089
00:50:45,400 --> 00:50:49,600
in only 10 days, so I'm really happy that Merv's okay.

1090
00:50:49,600 --> 00:50:51,600
I know that must be a big relief to you.

1091
00:50:51,600 --> 00:50:52,440
It really is.

1092
00:50:52,440 --> 00:50:54,960
I really shoulda, now upon hindsight,

1093
00:50:54,960 --> 00:50:56,680
maybe bought it a little bit,

1094
00:50:56,680 --> 00:50:58,880
like they give him a fishing boat back.

1095
00:51:00,360 --> 00:51:02,080
Like really kinda like set him up, you know,

1096
00:51:02,080 --> 00:51:03,400
cause he's a guy who deserves that.

1097
00:51:03,400 --> 00:51:06,039
He was just snatched off his boat while fishing.

1098
00:51:06,039 --> 00:51:08,559
Anyway, speaking of boats,

1099
00:51:08,559 --> 00:51:10,800
we should probably see if we can get on

1100
00:51:10,800 --> 00:51:11,760
one of these crews.

1101
00:51:11,800 --> 00:51:16,200
I assume being on a boat is very much like doing a caravan.

1102
00:51:18,160 --> 00:51:19,520
Yeah, that's probably true.

1103
00:51:19,520 --> 00:51:23,240
Don't we have to get some other things while we're here?

1104
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:27,840
Yeah, there was the shipment for the magic store owner.

1105
00:51:27,840 --> 00:51:30,040
Oh fuck, I didn't write that down.

1106
00:51:32,320 --> 00:51:34,280
Moon, you took some notes.

1107
00:51:34,280 --> 00:51:35,480
What are some things?

1108
00:51:36,440 --> 00:51:37,960
My notes literally just say,

1109
00:51:37,960 --> 00:51:40,080
steal stuff for the magic store owner.

1110
00:51:40,079 --> 00:51:41,960
Shipment from Aglarond.

1111
00:51:41,960 --> 00:51:45,039
You reach into your pocket in Sullivan's Sleight

1112
00:51:45,039 --> 00:51:48,559
and you pull out a list that was given to you.

1113
00:51:48,559 --> 00:51:50,920
Oh, hey, would you look at that?

1114
00:51:50,920 --> 00:51:53,199
You reverse pickpocketed me.

1115
00:51:53,199 --> 00:51:58,199
You unroll that list and on it is a literal list

1116
00:51:58,880 --> 00:52:03,400
of items that you are to find and bring back for Sharmy.

1117
00:52:05,079 --> 00:52:07,079
On the list, you see

1118
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:13,000
there is a circlet with runes written in infernal,

1119
00:52:14,880 --> 00:52:19,880
proximate size teacup saucer, red and green writing.

1120
00:52:20,920 --> 00:52:23,840
Also on the list, six alchemical jugs

1121
00:52:23,840 --> 00:52:26,079
marked with the sign of Dagon.

1122
00:52:27,840 --> 00:52:30,880
Also a selection of herbs

1123
00:52:31,880 --> 00:52:35,079
that have been shipped over from Aglarond.

1124
00:52:35,920 --> 00:52:40,920
Dream Flake, Sun Drop, Sitara, Goji Leaves and Sticksroot.

1125
00:52:42,239 --> 00:52:44,880
You know how much I don't want to get this stuff?

1126
00:52:44,880 --> 00:52:47,400
I know, I was hoping we could kind of just

1127
00:52:47,400 --> 00:52:49,319
get on a boat and get out of here.

1128
00:52:50,639 --> 00:52:54,199
But it looks like we've got some shopping

1129
00:52:54,199 --> 00:52:57,639
to do tomorrow or some.

1130
00:52:57,639 --> 00:52:59,559
We're gonna need better disguises.

1131
00:53:01,000 --> 00:53:01,840
Yeah.

1132
00:53:01,840 --> 00:53:04,519
I don't know, I'm kind of digging the sun hat.

1133
00:53:04,559 --> 00:53:05,920
The sun hat does look great.

1134
00:53:05,920 --> 00:53:07,239
It does change your look.

