Because you know that they're crazy.

1155
00:54:31,880 --> 00:54:32,719
Yep.

1156
00:54:32,719 --> 00:54:34,679
Like I remember being at like a street market

1157
00:54:34,679 --> 00:54:36,440
and there was these Hells Angels

1158
00:54:36,440 --> 00:54:40,280
and they came up to me and I was like 22.

1159
00:54:40,280 --> 00:54:42,039
I'm very excited for this story right now.

1160
00:54:42,039 --> 00:54:45,239
And I was drinking a bottle of water

1161
00:54:45,239 --> 00:54:46,800
and the guy's like,

1162
00:54:46,800 --> 00:54:48,880
"'Hey, can I have a sip of your water?'

1163
00:54:48,880 --> 00:54:50,199
And I'm like,

1164
00:54:50,199 --> 00:54:51,039
"'Yes?'

1165
00:54:53,039 --> 00:54:53,880
You just have the risk.

1166
00:54:53,880 --> 00:54:54,719
You could just have it.

1167
00:54:54,719 --> 00:54:55,559
Yes, exactly.

1168
00:54:55,559 --> 00:54:56,400
It's yours now.

1169
00:54:56,400 --> 00:54:58,079
I was like, yep, you bet.

1170
00:54:58,119 --> 00:55:00,480
And he was like, takes a big drink

1171
00:55:00,480 --> 00:55:04,400
and he's like this huge intimidating, scary man.

1172
00:55:04,400 --> 00:55:05,239
And he's like,

1173
00:55:05,239 --> 00:55:06,079
"'Oh, here you go.'

1174
00:55:06,079 --> 00:55:07,039
And I'm like,

1175
00:55:08,279 --> 00:55:09,119
and I was like,

1176
00:55:09,119 --> 00:55:10,239
"'No, no, you just keep it.

1177
00:55:10,239 --> 00:55:11,079
That's great.'

1178
00:55:11,079 --> 00:55:11,920
And he's like,

1179
00:55:11,920 --> 00:55:13,319
"'Well, you don't want it back now?'

1180
00:55:13,319 --> 00:55:14,159
And I'm like,

1181
00:55:15,119 --> 00:55:15,960
"'Oh no, I'll take it back.

1182
00:55:15,960 --> 00:55:16,799
Yeah, it's fine.'

1183
00:55:16,799 --> 00:55:17,799
"'Okay, no, I'll take it back.

1184
00:55:17,799 --> 00:55:18,639
I'm glad you had a drink.

1185
00:55:18,639 --> 00:55:19,759
Okay, bye.'"

1186
00:55:19,759 --> 00:55:22,360
Just like try to merge into the crowd.

1187
00:55:22,360 --> 00:55:23,199
But it's, yeah.

1188
00:55:23,199 --> 00:55:24,519
So it's like,

1189
00:55:24,519 --> 00:55:27,960
that's an unreasonable thing to ask a stranger.

1190
00:55:28,800 --> 00:55:30,240
And it's so unsettling.

1191
00:55:30,240 --> 00:55:32,240
I'm unsettled right now.

1192
00:55:32,240 --> 00:55:33,760
I feel like Russ put it in here

1193
00:55:33,760 --> 00:55:34,599
because he was like,

1194
00:55:34,599 --> 00:55:35,800
well, this is gonna freak Amy out.

1195
00:55:35,800 --> 00:55:38,760
It's just, I don't like it.

1196
00:55:38,760 --> 00:55:39,800
That's fair.

1197
